{"tid":924673,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哥迪奧拿迎接執教生涯400場勝利，勝率高達73.7%。","createTime":"2018-12-02T09:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T12:04:07.000Z","uid":143284,"like":38,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"712c5597d1234ad2d03ddeeef20ce21da263f01c","tid":924673,"uid":143284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T09:38:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://voice.hupu.com/soccer/2368640.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvoice.hupu.com%2Fsoccer%2F2368640.html&d=Qx2xuUP7W70gsE4E%2BeShXbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=1a2321d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://voice.hupu.com/soccer/2368640.html</a><br />\n<br />\n虎撲新聞12月2日訊 剛剛結束的英超比賽中，曼城在主場3-1戰勝了般尼茅夫，英超14輪比賽過後積38分繼續保持領跑。<br />\n而這場勝利也是主帥哥迪奧拿執教生涯中的第400場勝利，此前哥帥在執教巴塞時獲得了179場勝利，執教拜仁時則是124場，這也是哥迪奧拿在曼城的第97場勝利。<br />\n哥帥一共帶上述三支球隊踢了543場比賽，這也意味著哥帥整個執教生涯的勝率高達73.7%。"},{"pid":"f8cfa9d8fa5c68503af4324a98cb93637907dc09","tid":924673,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T10:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8582114a905ebc6ba5c197c06f1dedb484804230","tid":924673,"uid":38548,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T10:04:42.000Z","msg":"玩FM 都未必高過佢"},{"pid":"84a34989d21908afd8e53f578583a5614ecebe55","tid":924673,"uid":143284,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"8582114a905ebc6ba5c197c06f1dedb484804230","tid":924673,"uid":38548,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T10:04:42.000Z","msg":"玩FM 都未必高過佢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T10:05:25.000Z","msg":"但唔知點解fm入面佢成日輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c45b993356d9c262fa6d44a1203b58d1d71e3de","tid":924673,"uid":191762,"like":9,"dislike":37,"score":-28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T10:05:32.000Z","msg":"以佢教嗰啲波嚟講算低"},{"pid":"d3d994cd823949d03866dbe9a5ef489cf022985